name: Modern Luxe 4BR/4BA Retreat in East Riverside, Aus
description:
Discover the epitome of luxury living in this stunning 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom 2nd flr apartment nestled in the heart of East Riverside, Austin, TX. This upscale short-term rental is meticulously designed to offer a seamless blend of comfort and style, providing an unforgettable retreat for your stay.

As you step into this spacious haven, be greeted by an open-concept layout adorned with chic furnishings and modern decor. The living area is a perfect gathering spot, featuring plush large seating.

name: Downtown garden cottage
description: Quintessential Austin.  Tiny, private, rustic cottage 3 blocks to downtown in a garden setting- walk to breakfast tacos, coffee shops, restaurants, bars, music and galleries in the heart of the east side arts district. Clean. Quiet. Zen. Tons of birds, 2 friendly goats, a well-mannered dog, a playful cat and a dinosaur tortoise sometimes share the yard. Smoke-free. Easy walk to Austin Convention Center, Rainey St, SXSW, Hike and Bike, Ladybird Lake, 6th St.

name: Metric Modern space close to Tech Ridge & Domain
description: This modern condo offers easy access to all the highways and within walking distance to parks as well as craft breweries. Tech ridge blvd is only a few minutes away with all the California companies moving to Austin. Domain is less than 10 minutes and downtown is only 20 minutes away. There is a laundry across the street in the strip mall and parking is along the street in front of the condo. First floor condo with greenbelt in the back. Great location!

name: Charming private room with bathroom in East Austin
description:
Charming private room and private bathroom in East Austin with walk-in closet and on-site parking located on country club creek trail, steps from Lady Bird and major attractions.

Mini fridge, microwave, desk, steamer, kettle, radio, white noise machine, and printer are available.

Steps from bus stop (300 and 672)

name: Emos by AvantStay | Near 6th St in DT Austin
description:
- 33-story condo building
- Yoga room
- Shared pool on the rooftop
- Bright living area with a city view
- Modern kitchen and open spaced
- Fitness center
- Shared work-from-home space
- Ping pong table
- Outdoor dining and seating lounges

name: East DT condo w/private patio skyline view & more
description: studio condo in the booming Eastside. lots of walkable bars, restaurants, shops. one free parking spot in the complex lot and lots of free street parking nearby. private balcony other beautiful views of downtown Austin, UT tower, and UT Austin football stadium. a beautiful place to enjoy Austin

name: Cozy Home in Highland Neighborhood
description:
Private room with connected private bathroom/shower in lovely home located in quiet neighborhood near downtown Austin. Close to public transportation, light rail station, shopping, restaurants and entertainment. Free WIFI and private flat screen TV.



STR#125614

name: Cozy Tarrytown Condo Mins from Downtown & Zilker
description:
Escape to our cozy condo in the heart of Austin! Open, light, split-level condo is minutes to downtown Austin or Lake Austin.

Tarrytown, one of Austin's most coveted neighborhoods, is right outside your door. Walking distance to ATX favorites such as Lions Municipal Golf Course, HEB, Mozarts Coffee Shop, Pool Burger (cocktails & burgers), Deep Eddy Pool, and access to Lady Bird Lake Trail. Minutes away from 6th street.

This 2/1.5 condo can accommodate up to 4 guests comfortably.

name: Tarrytown 4bed/3.5bath 50' pool, 2 cats
description:
4 bedroom, 3.5 bath 4,000 square foot Tarrytown home, close to downtown and lakes. Cool off in our 50 foot pool w/ travertine deck, enjoy our outdoor eating area. Home gym w/ bike, treadmill, squat rack, bench, leg press, over 450 pounds of plates plus dumbbells. Cool travertine floors downstairs, hardwood upstairs, carpet in the bedrooms. Primary bedroom downstairs, three bedrooms upstairs.

Rent well below market rate because renters look after our two, friendly, hypo-allergenic cats.

name: South Park Meadows Calm Space
description:
Our lovely home is the perfect place to be close to all the things you need, 15 minutes from the city, and has a wonderful backyard. We are open to long term stays.
Me and my partner love meeting new people and sharing our love for Austin.
Common spaces are open for guests to use and we hope you’ll find our plant filled back porch a perfect place for relaxing during your travels.

name: SoCo 2BR corner suite w/ pool, king bed, fast WiFi
description:
Welcome to your new home in South 1st/SoCo - a true gem of the city with a diverse selection of food, entertainment, and outdoor activities.

Our 950 sqft 2-bedroom apartment is pet-friendly (pet fees apply) comes standard with a fully-stocked kitchen, dedicated work space, large bedrooms, community pool, washer and dryer, fast wifi, & dog park to accommodate you in the modern times.

► Downtown - 8 min.
► Zilker Park (ACL) - 12 min.
► Barton Creek Greenbelt - 8 min.
► Airport - 8 min.

name: Modern 1 Bed Guest House 3 blocks to Historic SoCo
description: 1 Bed Guest house (built in Nov 2016) in back of Main House that provides a perfect location for couples.  Located in a historic neighborhood, Travis Heights,  that is off of a quiet street and 3 blocks off of South Congress (near Torchys).  The guest house has an open floor plan with stained concrete floors, full bath and a kitchenette.   Dogs are welcome, but limited.  There is a gated back yard for your dogs to run around and a park down the street. New queen size mattress . POOL NOT INCLUDED

name: Pvt Room with Tv in House w Sunroom, Patio access
description: Relax in your cozy room with TV and private bathroom, then explore the house's sunroom, patio, and hammock. Enjoy comfort and tranquility in this inviting home away from home.

name: Charming Cozy Retreat with Garage -Near Airpt & DT
description:
This cozy new-build modern home is located in a central location near Austin's Airport ✈️, Downtown 🏙, Zilker Park 🏟️ , and Lady Bird Lake . This charming retreat features free parking in a private garage with an EV charging option 🚗, free washer and dryer 🧺, and a spacious private yard. With its proximity to the airport and downtown, you'll have easy access to Austin's vibrant attractions. Experience comfort and convenience in our lovely home.

We love healthcare workers and accommodate 3

description: Perfect Corporate Housing. Tesla and Samsung Contractors, please contact me for special discount

name: 7 BR Compound! 2 Homes in 1- PingPong - Yard Games
description:
This listing is for 2 homes that are BACK TO BACK. Great for large families/multiple families. You can open up the back fence gate and walk between the two houses. Both houses are stylish - with a backyard office & ping-pong table. Both homes have washer/dryer in unit and can fit 2 cars in each driveway with plenty of street parking.
This is a quiet neighborhood with friendly neighbors - an excellent place to relax! It’s only a 15 min drive to downtown, Zilker Park, Barton Springs Pool.

description:
Get the best out of Austin!
- Seconds from Town Lake and Downtown
- Walk to Bars and Food

The Eastsider is a beautifully updated craftsman bungalow offering 3 bedrooms, a luxury kitchen, and a breezy outdoor space.

Austin is known for its quirky nature and hodgepodge of musical and cultural tastes — and you can see it all from the comfort of the resort. You’re conveniently located just minutes from local attractions, diverse eateries, and vibrant venues.

description:
This stylish place to stay is perfect for your trips! This spacious 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath home boasts with full kitchen, dining table, living room, and a WFH setup- everything you need for an amazing stay! Take your mornings slow sipping your coffee and dine outside alfresco under the covered patio table!

Note, this is where I live, so my things will be present, so I will be selective and careful to find respectful people :)

name: Luxury yacht w/ paddle board & sound system!
description:
*This listing is for overnight stays only. Contact us for pricing for chartered rides!*

Are you looking for a unique stay? Welcome aboard our exquisite 40ft luxury yacht, tucked away in a lovely Marina on Lake Travis. You will experience serenity during the week, but on the weekends, the Marina is lively as the commercial boats charter hundreds of groups on yachts, pontoons & more! Whether you prefer to retreat from the world, or if you like to be part of the action, this is the place for you!

name: Downtown Austin Resort Condo @ 2 BR
description: Austin is known for its quirky nature and hodgepodge of musical and cultural tastes — and you can see it all from the comfort of the resort. You’re conveniently located just minutes from local attractions, diverse eateries, and vibrant venues.

name: Sun Bright 4 BR 3B, 7 Beds Sleeps 13 -North Austin
description:
Come and Enjoy your peaceful stay at our Sunshine Yellow Onyxa House. Loacated a stonethrow away from Major Highways I35 and 45 , this property is a peaceful abode that our family has put together to suit your needs.

We are detail oriented and go the extra mile and take pride in being able to meet and exceed your needs when we have you as our guest.

Two Storey house with three bedrooms upstairs and one bedroom on the First floor. This property is infectiously joyful and lit - Check yourself!

name: 2 Bedroom Presidential Suite in Downtown Austin
description:
Austin, Texas, is known for its quirky nature and hodgepodge of musical and cultural tastes. You won’t find any cowboys or ranges filled with cattle in this city — instead, you’ll marvel at the glittering lights of this small-scale metropolis. A stay in the city has its perks, too. Wyndham Austin is just a half-mile stroll from the State Capitol and you’ll discover vibrant venues, diverse eateries and incredible creativity everywhere. Austin makes a big impression!

Parking is $30 FYI

name: Stylish Stay Fully Fenced Back Yard 3Bed Sleeps 6
description: Welcome to our charming house nestled in the heart of S Austin! This spacious 3-bedroom retreat offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step into a cozy living area, tastefully decorated with modern touches and ample natural light. The fully equipped kitchen invites you to create, while the dining area provides a lovely space to share meals. Relax in the privacy of the fenced yard, ideal for outdoor gatherings. 3 Bedrooms with plush queen beds and 2 bathrooms with all the essentials!

name: Cottage #5 with onsite Saltwater Pool and Cafe
description:
Visit www.waybackaustin.com for more information on what The Wayback offers!

We love our beautiful, urban Austin, but also truly appreciate a little escape to the Texas Hill Country where it’s quieter, the air is fresh and time slows. The Wayback is a casual boutique hotel 15 minutes west of downtown. Our style here is friendly, comfortable and classic. Surrounded by hills and a big Texas sky, The Wayback is a place to feel the breeze, be carefree and linger.

name: Cozy Room in the Best Neighborhood in Austin
description: Your own private room just a few minutes away from the cafes, shops and food trucks of 1st Street – the space is conveniently located on the edge of Downtown, with all the quirks and perks of living in Austin. Take a 15-minute ride down to Barton Springs Beach for SUP, find live music in Congress (the neighborhood next door), or take it easy and hang out at home.

name: South Austin Casa Sparkling clean/super cute.
description: Clean, charming 3-1 located in the heart of Austin in a quiet neighborhood.  Minutes from Zilker Park and Downtown, to vibrant So. 1st and So. Congress. New granite counter kitchen, 2 living rooms, washer/dryer.  Enjoy shaded zero scape yard on lounge chairs or picnic table. Just installed fastest internet.

name: Lrg 2 Bd/2Bth Tanglewood Condo.
Wyndham Austin 2 Bedroom Deluxe
description:
Austin is known for its quirky nature and hodgepodge of musical and cultural tastes — and you can see it all from the comfort of the resort. You’re conveniently located just minutes from local attractions, diverse eateries, and vibrant venues.

Pictures used are stock photos and may not be exact room but room layout is the same. Must be 21 to check in. Paid parking is available on site for $30 daily. Resort will collect to put on file for incidentals at check in.

name: Amaryllis - super private, cozy, shaded, pets ok.
description:
Amaryllis is a Greek word for splendor or sparkling. That’s what you receive with this Classic Airstream set in a private, shaded location at Hudson Bend Ranch.

Our newest listing, Amaryllis offers a relaxed getaway from the crowds and noise of the city. Immerse yourself in nature as wild birds and our local deer family join you for morning coffee. Get a glimpse of Mr and Mrs Roadrunner making their morning rounds as the morning sun starts to penetrate the overhanging canopy. True splendor.

name: Landing | Spectacular 1BD, Clubhouse, Game Room
description:
Bristol Heights is a sought-after property where Landing offers fully furnished 1-bedroom, 2-bedroom, and 3-bedroom apartments stocked with everything you need to feel at home.

Bristol Heights is in a community that includes a Fitness Center, a Storage, and a Grilling Stations. Bristol Heights is in a car-dependent area, with a Walk Score of 50, a Transit Score of 24, and a Bike Score of 28.

name: Cheerful Home in The Hills
description: A 1950’s built spacious house with comfortable furniture and nice decor near Downtown and Mueller in a quiet neighborhood.

name: Modern Townhouse Close To Downtown- Great Location
description:
Best Location in Austin!

This listing is a new remodel within 5-10 minutes of downtown. Perfect location with everything a short bike/walk/drive away!

I am posting this listing as my actual home. I rent this space out as I travel very often. With that said, this house has everything you would ever need plus some!

name: Treehouse Condo
description: 2 story condo in a quiet gated community. High ceilings and big skylight give the unit lots of natural light throughout the day. Great balcony overlooking the Austin greenbelt. Walking distance to ACL and a short cab ride to downtown!

name: 106- studio you can get to all fun spots in 5 min
description:
Escape the everyday routine in this 1st floor studio located in the HEART of Austin. With amazing walkability & convenient public transportation access, this studio provides all the essentials so you can enjoy this city without worrying about where to do laundry and parking (included!)
**Limos offered at discounted prices when booked through us!**

Driving:
-5 min to UT Campus
-7min to Zilker|ACL
-15min from Austin Airport for easy arrival/departures

name: Breathtaking view | 6 beds | designer villa
description:
Wake up every morning to a breathtaking view of Austin's hills. We want your stay to feel luxurious, relaxing, and personalized.

The layout & bedding accommodations are perfect for 2 families to vacation together (2 rooms can serve as primary bedrooms). We want Ledge Mountain to feel like your home away from home.

Although you might want to cozy up and never leave, this prime location has you 15 minutes away from anywhere you'd want to go!

name: Luxury East Austin at its Finest near Downtown!
description: Welcome to fabulous East Austin! This house is within walking distance to dozens of Austin's best restaurants, coffee shops, bars and activities. You'll be in the heart of it all - three blocks to Town Lake and less than five minutes to 6th Street, downtown or Rainey Street. This luxury property has a spacious open layout with a newly completed backyard oasis, including a large heated pool with loungers to catch some sun or enjoy the oversized covered patio featuring a premium outdoor kitchen.

name: Elmer’s
description: Hi! I am Elmer, another tech company employee in Austin. 😉 This my main south Austin residence. Life gets boring for my dog and myself so I wanted to turn the master bedroom into a guest room. My dog Aspen will jump on you to show lovin’s. 🐕 Hope you don’t mind.

name: Beau Place-professional stays
description: This special place is close to everything, making it easy to plan your visit whether it is for work, pleasure, or both. Please note- this is a non-smoking property.

name: Sky-High Condo, Best DT View, Walkable, Convention
description:
Perched on the 22nd floor, this stylish and comfy condo boasts floor-to-ceiling windows with unbeatable views of downtown Austin, Town Lake, Auditorium Shores, and the bustling life of West 6th Street.

Central to Austin hotspots and walkable to music venues, shows, restaurants, nightlife, conventions, and parks. Including SXSW and ACL.

Incredible onsite amenities include onsite concierge, 24hr gym, rooftop infinity pool and sundeck, outside BBQ, dog park, business lounge, and trash butler.

name: Nature's Retreat Austin Hillside Home 10 Min to DT
description: Welcome to my home in West Lake Hills. Here, nature is all around, yet you're near downtown. Inside, you'll find a comfortable space filled with natural light, fully equipped kitchen, and cozy bedrooms. Step outside to a private patio and spacious backyard. Located in the peaceful West Lake, it's just a quick 8-minute drive to downtown Austin. Come to experience nature and city life together at this comfy retreat.

name: East Austin Cozy Getaway
description:
Our home and guest suite are 1 mile East of downtown on East Cesar Chavez. If you want to stay in the heart of Austin and prefer the character of an Airbnb, our suite is perfect for you! We are a mere 3 blocks from Lady Bird Lake and the hike & bike trail, & walking distance from numerous bars & restaurants.

*Note* The house is on a 2 lane street with auto & pedestrian traffic. Urban location, so please do not book if you need silence.

name: SoCo Sanctuary-Hidden Oasis in Heart of Austin
description:
• IDEAL B+B in the Heart of Austin. Walk to iconic clubs, restaurants, live music, shopping, museums, parks, pools, hiking, bat-viewing.
• Quiet - Clean - Safe OASIS in historic SoCo (SOuth COngress), this HIDDEN GEM-Wildlife Sanctuary awaits.
• Fabulous guest-house for 1-3 travelers. Private, park-like setting under giant oaks w/relaxing pond area - great for birding and YOU. Thoughtful items. Unscented sheets/towels. High-Speed internet. WELCOME!

name: South Congress Farmhouse
description:
South Congress has transformed into one of the most unique & fun destinations in Austin. Shopping from cowboy boots to Hermes & everything in between. Food from Tex-Mex to sushi & everything on between.

Music? Some of the best venues in Texas.

Walk to coffee at Joe’s, lunch at HopDoody, Margarita’s at Guerro’s, Seafood at Pearla's. Have a glass of wine poolside at San Jose then music at the Continental Club.

The perfect day in Austin and a day that’s all within 4 blocks of the front door!

name: Trendy South Congress Treehouse Studio
description: Feel as if climbing a beanstalk while walking up the oak-side stairs to the front door. Featuring bold and sometimes whimsical details, this elevated space has been featured in popular style sites, as well as on Austin's and Tribeza's Home Tours.

name: Walnut Creek Pool Paradise | Near The Domain
description:
Immerse yourself in comfort and style. Our home boasts sleek, modern décor and high-end amenities, ensuring a stay that's as comfortable as it is unforgettable.

· 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms for peaceful rest
· An Austin-themed kitchen for culinary inspiration
· A unique vinyl room boasting a vast record collection
· A backyard oasis with a pool, lounge, fireplace, and grill

In our home, you're not just staying in Austin—you're becoming a part of it. Welcome to your dream vacation.

name: Agave House
description:
This special place is close to everything, making it easy to plan your visit.

Great location. Place includes a outdoor Cowboy pool that can be both heated and cooled.

name: Sunny private master bedroom & bath in S. Austin
description:
You’ll have a private entrance to the master bedroom and bath in this quiet, walkable neighborhood. We’re a stone's throw from a quick bus to Zilker Park or downtown.
Wake up & enjoy coffee on the porch, or walk around the corner to one of Austin's favorite breakfast spots.
After a day exploring, come back to relax and grab take-out down the street from a local restaurant or food trailer.

name: Penny’s Palace
description: Dubbed Penny's Palace after their beloved retriever, this super spacious home is located in University Hills and offers the perfect mix of work, play and relaxation.  Experience desert charm in this modern, clean and comfy tri level home!  If you want to bear the Texas heat, lounge in the oversized fenced backyard complete with a hammock, outdoor BBQ/dining, and cowboy pool to soak.  Location is everything - fast and easy to hop on Hwy 183 or 290 to access the major highways to any part of ATX!
